##red|**Tony Catalano##**: I get you wanted to travel lately, but did you really have money to fly to Japan? And why did you go when it was so close to spring break? Did you even get permission for this?


##green|**Leonora Morales##**: Yeah, seriously. I mean, fuck you Vincent, paid off  [[[scp-005-vn|your debt]]] yet?


##blue|**Vincent Bohart##**: I had some stuff in my savings, so it was //daijoubu//.


##orange|**Noah Patel**##: So you went to Japan for almost half a month and now you‚Äôre starting to use words from there in your everyday vocabulary?! Guys, he's turned into a weeaboo, down bad.
